org.sat4j.pb.multiobjective

インタフェース IMultiObjOptimizationProblem

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    IOptimizationProblem, IProblem, RandomAccessModel
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    AbstractLinMultiObjOptimizer, LeximinDecorator, MinSumOWAOptimizer, OrderedObjsOWAOptimizer, SumLeximinDecompositionOWAOptimizer

    public interface IMultiObjOptimizationProblem
extends IOptimizationProblem
    A solver which implements this interface must be able to handle multiple objective functions. The inherited setObjectiveFunction(...) method should call addObjectiveFunction(...)
